{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_12", "eventName": "驚霆無聲", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "12-18", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "晚安", "storyInfo": "戈爾丁在變形者集群的見證下死去。重傷的貝爾德也獨自一人走向了生命的終結。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g3_school_indoor", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝你，變形者，你答應了我的懇求。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是什麼棘手的願望。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很巧，我們剛從一些更討厭的事情中騰出手來。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "教室，你最終還是邀請我們來到了這裡。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "合情合理，戈爾丁，你畢竟是一位老師，你始終都是這麼認為的。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，我今天會死在這裡。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還是做了這個決定。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊托會傷心的。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須要這麼做。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你為什麼如此糾結於這一點？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，我為什麼如此糾結於這一點？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我放不下孩子們，我擔心他們在這個時代中會找不到自己的去向，我放不下茉莉，她是個好姑娘，但她不明白如何保護自己。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，還有海蒂......但我辜負了她，我只願她不要怨恨我。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這大概很難吧，那麼多人因我而死。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我該承受這種怨恨。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戈爾丁，你知道，這種死亡無法改變任何事。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實話，這讓我們困惑......", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#2$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我們經歷的漫長時光中，擁抱死亡的人並不鮮見，可每次目睹我們仍然會感到不解。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#2$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們熟悉這些詞彙，“犧牲”“懺悔”“愧疚”，也許還有別的。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#2$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後的結局總是通向死亡。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#2$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很抱歉，在我們看來，這十分徒勞，死亡沒什麼意義，不值得迷戀。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#10$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死了就是死了而已。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，變形者，我很明白你說的這些話。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我想彌補那些死去的自救軍戰士，更好的選擇或許是繼續活下去，照顧那些受到了傷害的家庭，為他們盡一份力。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，我知道，我沒法做到，我沒辦法面對......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很害怕。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至死亡都比這種恐懼要輕鬆嗎？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#10$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一直在後退......我以為只要避讓開那些浪潮，我就仍能保住我的生活。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是退到哪一步我們才會承認舊的生活已經崩潰？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......退到哪一步才會承認舊的生活其實從未存在？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有辦法面對這些，我寧願在還未徹底絕望之前死去。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "變形者，給我個騙自己的機會吧。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#9$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humanchange", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "37_i11", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "yFrom": 20.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 40.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您變成了我的樣子，變形者。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別誤會，戈爾丁，我們沒有那麼喜歡自己的工作。我們不會去欺騙那些你珍重的人。", "name": "“戈爾丁”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只是，想要更好地體會你的感情。", "name": "“戈爾丁”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種感情確實很難理解，我們只能去感受。", "name": "“戈爾丁”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你曾問過我該如何生活。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我又怎麼可能知道。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，當我真正發現自己的無力的時候，放棄也是一種選擇，不是嗎？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊托也曾說起過這個詞，放棄。", "name": "“戈爾丁”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不是放棄自己，隨波逐流。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而是放棄生活本身。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說，“放棄生活本身”。", "name": "“戈爾丁”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些經歷......無論是愉悅的，還是痛苦的，沒必要緊攥著不放，對吧。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特別是，你發現自己走入了一座迷宮之中，而建築迷宮牆壁的，正是這些經歷。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這實在算不上抗爭，這是懦弱者的選擇。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我......起碼不會再次站在他們那邊了，對吧。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......已經很睏了。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "“戈爾丁”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "晚安，戈爾丁。", "name": "“戈爾丁”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_mini02_victoria_street_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒力氣了。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也好，我確實已經......足夠累了。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#2$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，最起碼最後的日子裡，格拉斯哥幫又團聚了。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#2$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......希望他們能安全離開。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝爾德踉蹌地走到一堵牆邊，緩緩坐了下來，在背後的牆上拉出一道長長的血痕。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的手已經開始麻木，她想要握起拳頭，但是不太成功。"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖......死確實比我想像的還要疼一些。起碼比在下巴接漢娜一拳要疼。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她轉過頭，身側不遠處，躺倒著一具屍體，瘦小而乾癟，看樣子已經死了有些日子。"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她突然發現，這具屍體有些面熟。"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“下個院士”先生，原來你在這裡。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位膽怯的市民面前躺著一個肉罐頭，已經被吃得乾乾淨淨。"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝爾德眨了眨眼睛，似乎這個可憐人的身側有些奇怪的東西。從牆上，到地上......一些黑色的曲線？"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是一些文字，一些圖樣。"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝爾德這時才發現，他又撿了一支筆，一支破破爛爛的炭筆，遠不及他的寶貝鋼筆體面。"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她摸了摸自己的口袋。本屬於紋章學家的裝飾精美的鋼筆仍在她手邊。可惜麥克拉倫沒認真讀這支華麗鋼筆最後寫下的那些文字。"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她艱難地拖著自己的身軀，往那些牆上文字的方向挪了挪，仔細辨認著這些細小的字跡。"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她笑了，忍不住咳嗽了起來。"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一篇申請皇家科學院院士頭銜的紋章學論文？", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，你最後寫下的就是這些東西？", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這毫無用處。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝爾德跳過牆上那些大段大段讓人不明就理的考證與闡釋。"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這篇論文沒有結尾，一片空白之後，這位先生憤怒地寫道，自己忘記了某些重要資料的內容。"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他應該是絕望了，停了好一會兒，筆跡淡了幾分。"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在某個時刻，這位膽怯的市民開始書寫起自己的願望。"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我希望《阿什沃思家族考》馬上出現在我的手邊。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我希望編輯們真正明白我工作的意義，並同意提高我的稿費。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 26.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我希望老師別生我的氣，那些只是學術爭論，我仍然尊敬他。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“好吧，如果有機會，我願意放棄學術爭論，再喝一次他泡的茶。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我還是很餓，想吃街角的那家炸鱗肉。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我希望簡沒有忘了我，我愛她，我仍像分開前一樣愛她。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我是個混蛋，我希望拳館的那些孩子沒事。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我想喝三百萬桶威士忌。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“薩朗姑姑，我想念你，我長大以後成了個壞孩子，對不起。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“該死的。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“該死的，誰來實現我的願望？我已經竭盡所能地祈禱了，向那些所有我知道和不知道的存在。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“如果現在那鼓吹律法的黎博利修士出現在我面前，我一定揍他一頓。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“好吧，好吧。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我希望所有人都能實現他們的願望，所有人都幸福快樂，所有人都能平安健康，所有人都能過上真正美好的生活，每一個人。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我希望再沒有人受苦，再沒有人被折磨，大家都應該笑，眼淚從這片大地上消失。餓肚子也消失。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我希望這一切沒有白費。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我希望這一切——”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "一道長長的劃痕後，筆跡在這裡消失。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#2$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，這就是最後了。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#2$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝爾德艱難地抬起手，這支鋼筆快乾了，她試了好幾次才留下一道短短的黑色墨跡。"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我也希望。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}